nodes.text: The Dockside Cafe was a dining establishment in Mos Eisley on Tatooine. It was a small restaurant and bar that was frequented by spacers. There was no gambling, but there was a live band, and a robo-bartender designated CG-X2R. Alfreda Goot baited Han Solo into the Cafe in an attempt to pick up the bounty on his head, but her mediocre training was no match for his luck, and she ended up dead.
